dc_title_s: Land Use St Croix County, WI 2016
dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents land use for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, St_Croix_LandUse_2016.gdb. [The current land use classification typically defined at the parcel level.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://sccgis-scccdd.opendata.arcgis.com/
